bon (page does not exist)">Gabon</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Trade_unions_in_The_Gambia&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Trade unions in The Gambia (page does not exist)">The Gambia</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Trade_unions_in_Ghana" title="Trade unions in Ghana">Ghana</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Trade_unions_in_Guinea&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Trade unions in Guinea (page does not exist)">Guinea</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Trade_unions_in_Guinea-Bissau&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Trade unions in Guinea-Bissau (page does not exist)">Guinea-Bissau</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Trade_unions_in_Kenya&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Trade unions in Kenya (page does not exist)">Kenya</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Trade_unions_in_Lesotho&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Trade unions in Lesotho (page does not exist)">Lesotho</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Trade_unions_in_Liberia&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Trade unions in Liberia (page does not exist)">Liberia</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Trade_unions_in_Libya&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Trade unions in Libya (page does not exist)">Libya</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Trade_unions_in_Madagascar&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Trade unions in Madagascar (page does not exist)">Madagascar</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Trade_un