s in Socotra (page does not exist)">Socotra</a> <small>(Yemen)</small>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Trade_unions_in_Somaliland&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Trade unions in Somaliland (page does not exist)">Somaliland</a></i>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Trade_unions_in_Southern_Sudan&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Trade unions in Southern Sudan (page does not exist)">Southern Sudan</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Trade_unions_in_Western_Sahara&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Trade unions in Western Sahara (page does not exist)">Western Sahara</a></i>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Trade_unions_in_Zanzibar&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Trade unions in Zanzibar (page does not exist)">Zanzibar</a> <small>(Tanzania)</small></span></p>
