ce:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Right_to_a_fair_trial" title="Right to a fair trial">Right to a fair trial</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Presumption_of_innocence" title="Presumption of innocence">Presumption of innocence</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Right_of_asylum" title="Right of asylum">Right of asylum</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Nationality" title="Nationality">Nationality</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Exile" title="Exile">Freedom from exile</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Privacy" title="Privacy">Privacy</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Freedom_of_thought" title="Freedom of thought">Freedom of thought and conscience</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Freedom_of_religion" title="Freedom of religion">Freedom of religion</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Freedom_of_speech" title="Freedom of speech">Freedom of expression</a> (<a href="/wiki/Freedom_of_information" title="Freedom of information">freedom of information</a>)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Freedom_of_assembly" title="Freedom of assembly">Freedom of assembly</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Freedom_of_association" title="Freedom of association">Freedom of association</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Right_to_protest" title="Right to protest">Right to protest</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Universal_suffrage" title="Universal suffrage">Universal suffrage</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Marriage" title="Marriage">Marriage</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href=